Il Festival Transeuropa ho lö mincha duos ans ed es ün evenimaint/forum/conferenza politica, culturela ed artistica chi reunescha bgers formats differents. Nus, l'organisaziun European Alternative chi sto davous, fains que uossa daspö 10 ans. Nus vains dimena già bgera experientscha. I's tratta d'ün evenimaint ambulant chi ho lö mincha vouta in üna otra cited. La davous vouta, avaunt duos ans, d'eirans a Belgrad, dimena in üna cited ourdvart l'Uniun Europeica. Quist an, 2017, vulaivans ir a Madrid per bgers motivs differents.
